        {
          "id": "tm-markdown",
          "type": "text",
          "content": "**Rich text** supports *italic*, `inline code`, ~~strikethrough~~, and [links](https://deckode.dev).\n\nInline math: the quadratic formula $x = \\frac{-b \\pm \\sqrt{b^2 - 4ac}}{2a}$ renders in text flow.",
          "position": { "x": 60, "y": 100 },
          "size": { "w": 840, "h": 60 },
          "style": { "fontSize": 16, "color": "#475569", "lineHeight": 1.6 }
        },
        {
          "id": "tm-bg",
          "type": "shape",
          "shape": "rectangle",
          "position": { "x": 40, "y": 175 },
          "size": { "w": 880, "h": 340 },
          "style": { "fill": "#1e293b", "borderRadius": 16 }
        },
        {
          "id": "tm-schrodinger",
          "type": "text",
          "content": "**Schr\u00f6dinger Equation**\n\n$$i\\hbar \\frac{\\partial}{\\partial t}\\Psi(\\mathbf{r},t) = \\left[-\\frac{\\hbar^2}{2m}\\nabla^2 + V(\\mathbf{r},t)\\right]\\Psi(\\mathbf{r},t)$$",
          "position": { "x": 60, "y": 190 },
          "size": { "w": 420, "h": 140 },
          "style": { "fontSize": 16, "color": "#e2e8f0", "lineHeight": 1.4 }
        },
        {
          "id": "tm-einstein",
          "type": "text",
          "content": "**Einstein Field Equations**\n\n$$R_{\\mu\\nu} - \\tfrac{1}{2}R\\,g_{\\mu\\nu} + \\Lambda g_{\\mu\\nu} = \\frac{8\\pi G}{c^4}T_{\\mu\\nu}$$",
          "position": { "x": 500, "y": 190 },
          "size": { "w": 400, "h": 140 },
          "style": { "fontSize": 16, "color": "#e2e8f0", "lineHeight": 1.4 }
        },
        {
          "id": "tm-maxwell",
          "type": "text",
          "content": "**Maxwell's Equations**\n\n$$\\nabla \\cdot \\mathbf{E} = \\frac{\\rho}{\\varepsilon_0}, \\quad \\nabla \\times \\mathbf{E} = -\\frac{\\partial \\mathbf{B}}{\\partial t}, \\quad \\nabla \\cdot \\mathbf{B} = 0, \\quad \\nabla \\times \\mathbf{B} = \\mu_0\\mathbf{J} + \\mu_0\\varepsilon_0\\frac{\\partial \\mathbf{E}}{\\partial t}$$",
          "position": { "x": 60, "y": 340 },
          "size": { "w": 840, "h": 80 },
          "style": { "fontSize": 16, "color": "#e2e8f0", "lineHeight": 1.4 }
        },
        {
          "id": "tm-matrix",
          "type": "text",
          "content": "**Matrix Multiplication**\n\n$$\\begin{pmatrix} a & b \\\\ c & d \\end{pmatrix} \\begin{pmatrix} e & f \\\\ g & h \\end{pmatrix} = \\begin{pmatrix} ae+bg & af+bh \\\\ ce+dg & cf+dh \\end{pmatrix}$$",
          "position": { "x": 60, "y": 430 },
          "size": { "w": 430, "h": 80 },
          "style": { "fontSize": 15, "color": "#e2e8f0", "lineHeight": 1.4 }
        },
        {
          "id": "tm-svd",
          "type": "text",
          "content": "**SVD Decomposition**\n\n$$A = U\\Sigma V^T = \\begin{bmatrix} u_1 & \\cdots & u_m \\end{bmatrix} \\begin{bmatrix} \\sigma_1 & & \\\\ & \\ddots & \\\\ & & \\sigma_r \\end{bmatrix} \\begin{bmatrix} v_1^T \\\\ \\vdots \\\\ v_n^T \\end{bmatrix}$$",
          "position": { "x": 500, "y": 430 },
          "size": { "w": 410, "h": 80 },
          "style": { "fontSize": 15, "color": "#e2e8f0", "lineHeight": 1.4 }
        }
      ]
    },
